            "y1": 857,
            "x2": 1158,
            "y2": 1009
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 4,
        "text": "सरस्वती के वरद पुत्र, सुन्दरता से मुखचन्द्र खिला ।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jagannatha1955_0001_textline_4.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 157,
            "y1": 1081,
            "x2": 1765,
            "y2": 1264
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 5,
        "text": "'पण्डितराज' खिताब उन्हें था दिल्ली के दरबार मिला ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jagannatha1955_0001_textline_5.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 173,
            "y1": 1217,
            "x2": 1765,
            "y2": 1357
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 6,
        "text": "यौवन में प्रभुत्व जो पाया, तबियत भी रंगीन हुई ।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jagannatha1955_0001_textline_6.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 154,
            "y1": 1328,
            "x2": 1774,
            "y2": 1449
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 7,
        "text": "ब्याहा एक शाहजादी को, यही चूक संगीन हुई ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jagannatha1955_0001_textline_7.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 152,
            "y1": 1416,
            "x2": 1776,
            "y2": 1552
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 8,
        "text": "दुलहिन ले काशी को लौटे कहीं न कुछ सत्कार हुआ ।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jagannatha1955_0001_textline_8.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 152,
            "y1": 1593,
            "x2": 1768,
            "y2": 1738
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 9,
        "text": "ब्राह्मणवंश सदा का त्यागी घर ही से बहिष्कार हुआ ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jagannatha1955_0001_textline_9.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 154,
            "y1": 1696,
            "x2": 1760,
            "y2": 1830
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 10,
        "text": "जी भर-भर सबको समझाया प्रायश्चित पूजा कीनी ।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jagannatha1955_0001_textline_10.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 154,
            "y1": 1791,
            "x2": 1792,
            "y2": 1915
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 11,
        "text": "धर्म सनातन के थे पक्के सभी ओर देखा झगड़ा ।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jagannatha1955_0001_textline_11.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 160,
            "y1": 2086,
            "x2": 1757,
            "y2": 2211
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 12,
        "text": "धर्ममूल श्रीगंग-चरण को आतुर होकर जा पकड़ा ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jagannatha1955_0001_textline_12.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 152,
            "y1": 2173,
            "x2": 1763,
            "y2": 2305
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 13,
        "text": "पूत कपूत निकल जाता है मातु कुमातु न होती है ।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jagannatha1955_0001_textline_13.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 149,
            "y1": 2271,
            "x2": 1749,
            "y2": 2405
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 14,
        "text": "फँसा विपद में, फिरूँ तिरस्कृत धर्म-मातु, क्या सोती है ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jagannatha1955_0001_textline_14.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 154,
            "y1": 2358,
            "x2": 1754,
            "y2": 2500
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 15,
        "text": "आराधन कर देवनदी का अति प्रसन्न उनको कीना ।",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jagannatha1955_0001_textline_15.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 149,
            "y1": 2559,
            "x2": 1765,
            "y2": 2691
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 16,
        "text": "खोज-खोजकर धर्मग्रन्थ उत्तर विरोधियों को दीना ॥",
        "image_path": "datasetProcessed/cropped_textlines/images/jagannatha1955_0001_textline_16.png",
        "bounding_box": {
            "x1": 141,
            "y1": 2647,
            "x2": 1754,
            "y2": 2785
        }
    },
    {
        "line_number": 17,
        "text": "फिर भी बढ़ता देख दुराग्रह कहा न हम बोलें ज्यादे ।",
